flowchart TD
    A["1. Evapotranspiration Drop
    MODIS (ET, NDVI)
    Reduced vegetation moisture and activity"]

    A -->|"↓ ET → ↓ clouds"| B

    B["2. Cloud Cover Decline
    MODIS, EUMETSAT
    Less vapor → fewer clouds"]

    B -->|"↓ clouds → ↑ OLR"| C

    C["3. OLR Increase
    CERES (8–13 μm)
    More radiation escapes due to less cloud cover"]

    C -->|"↑ OLR → ↓ condensation"| D

    D["4. Suppressed Latent Heat Flux
    MODIS, AIRS
    Less condensation means less energy release"]

    D -->|"↓ latent heat → ↓ pressure gradient"| E

    E["5. Flattened Pressure Gradient
    ERA5
    Weaker uplift and inflow circulation"]

    E -->|"↓ inflow → diverted moisture"| F

    F["6. Moisture Rerouting
    ERA5, Storm Tracks
    Moisture diverted to other regions"]

    F -->|"Positive feedback"| A

    style A fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style B fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style C fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style D fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style E fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#999,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style F fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#999,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
